data.description: Welcome to 410 W Vine St. This charming 3-bedroom home located in Wapakoneta is ready for new owners. The home offers a large living room, eat-in kitchen, master bedroom, and ensuite with a new shower and flooring on the first floor. The first level walls have been freshly painted white waiting for you to put your own touch on the home. The home offers a nice-sized laundry/mud room that gives you access to the patio and yard. The 2-car detached garage with plenty of extra room, fully insulated (including garage door and ceiling), 100amp 240v breaker box, heated with thermostat control, tornado maker 3000 fan for when it gets hot and a tire rack that fits 3 full sets. HVAC, water heater, and new pex water lines are done.  Call today to schedule a showing!
